{"tid":1633971,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"歐美心理學文獻: 無後果裝修行為會導致上癮並變本加厲","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T16:22:24.000Z","uid":294955,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a28d566634153f76bcb87bf21a1db96aacecbcea","tid":1633971,"uid":294955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:59:24.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;Vandalism permits powerless individuals to strike out against the institutions which control them and to take charge of the situation themselves, arousing fear in others and raising their own self-esteem. An inhibited person who acts aggressively and is not punished feels relieved and encouraged; psychologically, these pleasant feelings demand increasing reinforcement, escalating aggressive behavior. &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\nAbstract, &quot;Psychological Analysis of Vandalism&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncjrs.gov/App/Publications/abstract.aspx?ID=70758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncjrs.gov%2FApp%2FPublications%2Fabstract.aspx%3FID%3D70758&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4sF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=7c4a2a4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncjrs.gov/App/Publications/abstract.aspx?ID=70758</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果呢個係事實，執法者只要對裝修行為人士手軟，就會加快呢場抗爭運動走向失控並完全變質，最終坐享其成。</span></span>"},{"pid":"d2314bf639b3ccc72d7b34c1928871c1a08533ee","tid":1633971,"uid":132010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"928e7fafc101b956793249996d883792f585a6c7","tid":1633971,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2314bf639b3ccc72d7b34c1928871c1a08533ee","tid":1633971,"uid":132010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5ff162c7399eb2db4e7b1b30c8444c12e41eeb","tid":1633971,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:20:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"00f6c5833f50260b4e72881f6cfde124c50eab27","tid":1633971,"uid":143382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:22:24.000Z","msg":"只好靠自己人提醒同自我不停反思"}]}